channel.title: My development
channel.description:
Hi, I have not made a private server for quite a bit of time now. Learning PHP and mysql kinda got boring now I have quite a bit of knowladge on them.
But, I am going to develop a new private server, it is not going to be much. Basically it'll be a blank source.
[b]Server[/b] [i]The development has not started, I need to sort out my personal life out first, quite a few things have happend.[/i]
The server will include.
-All skills should be working 70 - 90% I will hold Tests to see if the server is stable, and skills are working without many glitches (Expect to see some glitches)
-Mini games will be created, there will not be a teleporting interface to get there, you will have to get there by walking. (Don't expect much mini-games, they will all work 100% so it'll take a bit to do that)
-Perfect IP ban
-Good fighting timers, don't see much servers that are pin point.
-All dragon specials, barrow specials will also be done if I have enough time.
-More suggestions please.
Nothing much, just to fix up a little bit of servers.
